#. module: pos_iot
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/pos_iot/static/src/app/utils/payment/payment_interface_iot.js:0
msgid ""
"The IoT Box cannot detect the payment terminal. Please check if the terminal"
" is still connected."
msgstr ""
"IoT Box ບໍ່ສາມາດກວດພົບເຄື່ອງຮູດບັດໄດ້. ກະລຸນາກວດສອບວ່າເຄື່ອງຮູດບັດຍັງເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຢູ່ຫຼືບໍ່."

#. module: pos_iot
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/pos_iot/static/src/app/utils/printer/iot_printer.js:0
msgid ""
"The IoT Box is connected, but the receipt printer isn't. In order to continue, ensure your printer is connected:\n"
"\n"
"1/ for USB printers, check the cable between the IoT Box and the receipt printer\n"
"2/ for network printers, ensure the printer is connected to the internet."
msgstr ""
"IoT Box ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ແລ້ວ, ແຕ່ເຄື່ອງພິມໃບບິນຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່. ເພື່ອດຳເນີນການຕໍ່, ໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າເຄື່ອງພິມຂອງທ່ານເ"
"ຊື່ອມຕໍ່ແລ້ວ:\n"
"\n"
"1/ ສຳລັບເຄື່ອງພິມ USB, ໃຫ້ກວດສອບສາຍເຄເບິນລະຫວ່າງ IoT Box ແລະ ເຄື່ອງພິມໃບບິນ\n"
"2/ ສຳລັບເຄື່ອງພິມເຄືອຂ່າຍ, ໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າເຄື່ອງພິມເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ອິນເຕີເນັດແລ້ວ."

#. module: pos_iot
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:pos_iot.field_res_config_settings__module_pos_iot_ingenico
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:pos_iot.res_config_view_form_inherit_pos_iot
msgid ""
"The transactions are processed by Ingenico via an IoT box. Setup your "
"terminal on the related payment method."
msgstr ""
"ທຸລະກຳຕ່າງໆແມ່ນຖືກປະມວນຜົນໂດຍ Ingenico ຜ່ານ IoT box. ຕັ້ງຄ່າເຄື່ອງຮູດບັດຂອງທ່ານໃນວິທີການຊຳລະເ"
"ງິນທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

#. module: pos_iot
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:pos_iot.field_res_config_settings__module_pos_iot_six
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:pos_iot.res_config_view_form_inherit_pos_iot
msgid ""
"The transactions are processed by Six via an IoT box. Setup your terminal on"
" the related payment method."
msgstr ""
"ທຸລະກຳຕ່າງໆແມ່ນຖືກປະມວນຜົນໂດຍ Six ຜ່ານ IoT box. ຕັ້ງຄ່າເຄື່ອງຮູດບັດຂອງທ່ານໃນວິທີການຊຳລະເງິນທີ່ກ່ຽ"
"ວຂ້ອງ."

#. module: pos_iot
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:pos_iot.field_res_config_settings__module_pos_iot_worldline
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:pos_iot.res_config_view_form_inherit_pos_iot
msgid ""
"The transactions are processed by Worldline via an IoT box. Setup your "
"terminal on the related payment method."
msgstr ""
"ທຸລະກຳຕ່າງໆແມ່ນຖືກປະມວນຜົນໂດຍ Worldline ຜ່ານ IoT box. ຕັ້ງຄ່າເຄື່ອງຮູດບັດຂອງທ່ານໃນວິທີການຊຳລະ"
"ເງິນທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

